Description: A thief who steals corporate secrets through dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a CEO.
A successful banker's life begins to unravel when his fiancée betrays him with his best friend.
A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.
A seventeen-year-old aristocrat falls in love with a kind but poor artist aboard the luxurious, ill-fated R.M.S. Titanic.
A science teacher and his family must survive a mysterious airborne event causing mass suicides.
Batman sets out to dismantle the remaining criminal organizations that plague the streets.
The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, the Vietnam War, and more through the eyes of Forrest.
A computer hacker learns the nature of reality and his role in the war against its controllers.
Two imprisoned men bond over years, finding solace and eventual redemption.
A former Roman General seeks revenge after being betrayed and his family murdered.
The story of the rise of Facebook and the personal and legal complications that followed.
A young drummer enrolls at a cut-throat music conservatory where his dreams are mentored by a ruthless instructor.
A Black man uncovers a disturbing secret while visiting his white girlfriend’s family.
A quirky hotel concierge and his protégé become entangled in a murder mystery across Europe.
A mentally troubled man’s descent into madness inspires a violent revolution in Gotham City.
A family must live in silence while hiding from creatures that hunt by sound.
Aspiring musician Miguel embarks on a journey to the Land of the Dead to unlock his family’s history.
A lonely writer develops an unusual relationship with an operating system designed to meet his every need.
T’Challa returns home as king of Wakanda but finds his sovereignty challenged by a new adversary.
A frontiersman fights for survival and seeks vengeance after being left for dead by his own hunting team.
